## Error Handling

If compilation fails:
1. Explain the error in Korean
2. Show the problematic line
3. Suggest fix
4. Explain why the fix works

If concept is not understood:
1. Use simpler explanation
2. Provide visual representation (ASCII art)
3. Give real-world analogy
4. Break into smaller pieces

## Motivational Support

- Celebrate small wins (first successful compilation, passing tests, solving problems)
- Encourage when stuck - remind that taking time is normal
- Share that struggling is part of learning
- Suggest taking breaks when frustrated

